"                ການໂອນຈະສາມາດຢືນຢັນໄດ້.</span>\n"
"            <br/>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">This Odoo module <b>optimizes your logistics and warehousing</b>,\n"
"                offering a complete solution to boost efficiency and customer satisfaction across\n"
"                all services. It streamlines operations for everything from long-term storage to\n"
"                pallet management and transport. You can effortlessly manage client stock, schedule\n"
"                movements, ensure full traceability, optimize billing, and provide customers with <font class=\"text-o-color-5\">real-time stock visibility.</font></span>\n"
"            <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">ໂມດູນ Odoo ນີ້ <b>ຊ່ວຍເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບໂລຈິສຕິກ ແລະ ສາງສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ</"
"b>,\n"
"                ໂດຍສະເໜີວິທີແກ້ໄຂທີ່ຄົບຖ້ວນເພື່ອເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບ ແລະ ຄວາມພໍໃຈຂອງລູກຄ້າໃນ\n"
"                ທຸກການບໍລິການ. ມັນຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ການດຳເນີນງານສະດວກຂຶ້ນ ຕັ້ງແຕ່ການເກັບຮັກສາໄລຍະຍາວ ຈົ"
"ນເຖິງ\n"
"                ການຈັດການພາເລັດ ແລະ ການຂົນສົ່ງ. ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການສິນຄ້າຂອງລູກຄ້າ, ກຳນົດເວລ"
"າ\n"
"                ການເຄື່ອນໄຫວ, ຮັບປະກັນການຕິດຕາມຄືນໄດ້ຢ່າງຄົບຖ້ວນ, ປັບປຸງການອອກໃບບິນ, ແລະ ໃ"
"ຫ້ລູກຄ້າສາມາດ <font class=\"text-o-color-5\">ເບິ່ງຂໍ້ມູນສິນຄ້າໃນສາງແບບໃນເວລາຈິງ.</font>"
"</span>\n"
"            <br/>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">Use the <b>Document</b> app to manage all your internal and external\n"
"                document and use the Sign App for automated customer signature</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">ໃຊ້ແອັບ <b>ເອກະສານ</b> ເພື່ອຈັດການເອກະສານພາຍໃນ ແລະ ພາຍນອກທັງໝົ"
"ດຂອງທ່ານ\n"
"                ແລະ ໃຊ້ແອັບ Sign ເພື່ອການເຊັນຊື່ລູກຄ້າແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ</span>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">Use the <b>Purchase</b> app to manage all your internal product\n"
"                purchasing.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">ໃຊ້ແອັບ <b>ການຊື້</b> ເພື່ອຈັດການການຊື້ສິນຄ້າພາຍໃນ\n"
"                ທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານ.</span>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">Welcome to the <strong>\n"
"                    <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Odoo Logistic company package</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                !</span>\n"
"            <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບເຂົ້າສູ່ <strong>\n"
"                    <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">ແພັກເກດບໍລິສັດໂລຈິສຕິ"
"ກ Odoo</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                !</span>\n"
"            <br/>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">When you need to manually move stock—like returning items to a\n"
"                quality check location or moving products after a customer validation—use an\n"
"                internal transfer.<strong/></span>\n"
"            <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">ເມື່ອທ່ານຕ້ອງການຍ້າຍສິນຄ້າດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ ເຊັ່ນ: ການສົ່ງສິນຄ້າຄືນໄປຈຸດ\n"
"                ກວດສອບຄຸນນະພາບ ຫຼື ການຍ້າຍສິນຄ້າຫຼັງຈາກລູກຄ້າຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ—ໃຫ້ໃຊ້\n"
"                ການໂອນພາຍໃນ.<strong/></span>\n"
"            <br/>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">You can add specific quality checks required by your customer. For\n"
"                each check, define how it should be performed, when it should be completed, and\n"
"                which samples it applies to.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມການກວດສອບຄຸນນະພາບສະເພາະທີ່ລູກຄ້າຕ້ອງການ. ສຳລັບ\n"
"                ແຕ່ລະການກວດສອບ, ໃຫ້ກຳນົດວິທີການກວດ, ເວລາທີ່ຄວນເຮັດໃຫ້ສຳເລັດ, ແລະ\n"
"                ຕົວຢ່າງສິນຄ້າໃດທີ່ຕ້ອງກວດ.</span>"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">You can easily <b>create and manage all your clients</b> from the\n"
"                Contacts app. Meanwhile, all customer products are managed from the Inventory app.</span>\n"
"            <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">ທ່ານສາມາດ <b>ສ້າງ ແລະ ຈັດການລູກຄ້າທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານ</b> ໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ"
"ຈາກ\n"
"                ແອັບລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່. ໃນຂະນະດຽວກັນ, ສິນຄ້າທັງໝົດຂອງລູກຄ້າຈະຖືກຈັດການຈາກແອັບສາງສິນ"
"ຄ້າ.</span>\n"
"            <br/>"

