#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If it's a new customer, their contact record can be created directly from the\n"
"                opportunity."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າເປັນລູກຄ້າໃໝ່, ລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ຂອງພວກເຂົາສາມາດສ້າງໄດ້ໂດຍກົງຈາກ\n"
"                ໂອກາດຂາຍ."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
