msgstr "ຖ້າເປັນການອອກໃບບິນຄັ້ງທຳອິດ:"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you have the <b>Lot numbers</b> available, you can add them by clicking on <b>\n"
"                Details</b> and then <b>Import Serials/Lots</b>."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານມີ <b>ໝາຍເລກລັອດ (Lot numbers)</b>, ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມພວກມັນໄດ້ໂດຍການຄລິກທີ່ <b>\n"
"                ລາຍລະອຽດ</b> ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນ <b>ນຳເຂົ້າໝາຍເລກຊີຣຽວ/ລັອດ</b>."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you need to manage more complex quality control processes, use the <b>quality\n"
"                            check spreadsheet</b>."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການຈັດການຂະບວນການຄວບຄຸມຄຸນນະພາບທີ່ສັບສົນກວ່າ, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ <b>ຕາຕະລາງ\n"
"                            ກວດສອບຄຸນນະພາບ</b>."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you place products in packs, you can use the automated shipping connection with\n"
"                external carriers."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານບັນຈຸສິນຄ້າໃສ່ໃນການບັນຈຸ (packs), ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ການຂົນສົ່ງແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດກັບ\n"
"                ຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການຂົນສົ່ງພາຍນອກ."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "If you've invoiced this customer before:"
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານເຄີຍອອກໃບບິນໃຫ້ລູກຄ້ານີ້ມາກ່ອນ:"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In the <b>Inventory App</b>, click on <b>Pick</b> and then <b>Create a new one</b>.\n"
"                (If your warehouse settings are configured for a one-step process, select <b>\n"
"                Delivery</b> instead.)"
msgstr ""
"ໃນ <b>ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ</b>, ຄລິກທີ່ <b>ຈັດສິນຄ້າ (Pick)</b> ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນ <b>ສ້າງໃໝ່</b>.\n"
"                (ຖ້າການຕັ້ງຄ່າສາງຂອງທ່ານຖືກກຳນົດເປັນຂະບວນການຂັ້ນຕອນດຽວ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <b>\n"
"                ການຈັດສົ່ງ (Delivery)</b> ແທນ.)"

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In the <b>Inventory App</b>, click on <b>Receipt</b> and then <b>Create a new one</b>\n"
"                ."
msgstr ""
"ໃນ <b>ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ</b>, ຄລິກທີ່ <b>ການຮັບສິນຄ້າ (Receipt)</b> ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນ <b>ສ້າງໃໝ່</b>"
"\n"
"                ."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "In the pop-up window, click <b>\"Grant Access.\"</b>"
msgstr "ໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມທີ່ປາກົດຂຶ້ນ, ຄລິກ <b>\"ໃຫ້ສິດເຂົ້າເຖິງ.\"</b>"

