#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once a receipt is confirmed, a storage operation is automatically created to put the\n"
"                product into stock."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອການຮັບສິນຄ້າໄດ້ຮັບການຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ, ການດຳເນີນງານການເກັບຮັກສາຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດເພື່ອເອົາ\n"
"                ສິນຄ້າເຂົ້າສາງ."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once all information is collected and approved by the client, create a new <b>\n"
"                Quotation</b>."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອເກັບກຳຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດ ແລະ ໄດ້ຮັບການອະນຸມັດຈາກລູກຄ້າແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ສ້າງ <b>\n"
"                ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ</b> ໃໝ່."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "Once validated, the delivery operation will be created."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ, ການດຳເນີນງານການຈັດສົ່ງຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
