#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Storage Report pulls data from <b>Inventory/Reporting/Stock History</b>."
msgstr ""
"ລາຍງານການເກັບຮັກສາດຶງຂໍ້ມູນມາຈາກ <b>ສາງສິນຄ້າ/ລາຍງານ/ປະຫວັດສາງສິນຄ້າ</b>."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The app streamlines the invoicing process for these\n"
"            agreements. Additionally, you can access reports on occupancy and dates to help\n"
"            anticipate and manage your storage capacity."
msgstr ""
"ແອັບຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຂະບວນການອອກໃບບິນສຳລັບຂໍ້ຕົກລົງເຫຼົ່ານີ້ສະດວກຂຶ້ນ.\n"
"            ນອກຈາກນັ້ນ, ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງລາຍງານກ່ຽວກັບການນຳໃຊ້ພື້ນທີ່ ແລະ ວັນທີ ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍ\n"
"            ຄາດການ ແລະ ຈັດການຄວາມຈຸຂອງສາງຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The barcode app can be installed as a\n"
"                        standalone application on devices. This means people can use it without\n"
"                        having access to the rest of the database."
msgstr ""
"ແອັບບາໂຄດສາມາດຕິດຕັ້ງເປັນ\n"
"                        ແອັບພລິເຄຊັນແຍກຕ່າງຫາກໃນອຸປະກອນຕ່າງໆ. ສິ່ງນີ້ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າພະນັກງານສາ"
"ມາດໃຊ້ມັນໄດ້\n"
"                        ໂດຍບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງເຂົ້າເຖິງສ່ວນອື່ນໆຂອງຖານຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid "The customer reminders."
msgstr "ການແຈ້ງເຕືອນລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The customer will then receive an email with instructions to create their "
"account."
msgstr "ຈາກນັ້ນລູກຄ້າຈະໄດ້ຮັບອີເມວພ້ອມຄຳແນະນຳໃນການສ້າງບັນຊີຂອງພວກເຂົາ."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The dashboard provides all the necessary information,\n"
"            including storage occupancy, completed transfers, created packages, and performed\n"
"            quality checks. You just need to manually adjust the quantities on your invoices using\n"
"            this data."
msgstr ""
"ກະດານຂໍ້ມູນໃຫ້ຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈຳເປັນທັງໝົດ,\n"
"            ລວມມີການນຳໃຊ້ພື້ນທີ່ເກັບຮັກສາ, ການໂອນທີ່ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ, ການບັນຈຸທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນ, ແລະ ການກວດສ"
"ອບ\n"
"            ຄຸນນະພາບທີ່ດຳເນີນການແລ້ວ. ທ່ານພຽງແຕ່ຕ້ອງປັບຈຳນວນໃນໃບບິນຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ\n"
"            ໂດຍໃຊ້ຂໍ້ມູນເຫຼົ່ານີ້."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
