"You can print <b>barcode commands</b> to\n"
"                        streamline your operations with quick scanning actions."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດພິມ <b>ຄຳສັ່ງບາໂຄດ</b> ເພື່ອ\n"
"                        ໃຫ້ການດຳເນີນງານຂອງທ່ານສະດວກຂຶ້ນດ້ວຍການສະແກນຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ວ່ອງໄວ."

#. module: 3pl_logistic_company
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:3pl_logistic_company.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries &gt;\n"
